<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Online Premium Payment</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f2f2f2;
    text-align: center;
}

/* Top Logo Section */
.header {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 25px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
}

.header img {
    height: 65px;
}

/* Main Section */
.container {
    margin-top: 40px;
}

.main-title {
    color: #e31837;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.subtitle {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

/* Input Box */
.input-box {
    width: 320px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 5px;
    outline: none;
}

.input-box::placeholder {
    color: #999;
}

/* Button */
.btn {
    display: block;
    margin: 20px auto;
    background-color: #0b5c8e;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 28px;
    font-size: 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.btn:hover {
    background-color: #084a72;
}

/* Footer Text */
.footer {
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 50px auto;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

.footer strong {
    font-weight: bold;
}

.footer a {
    color: #e31837;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.footer ul {
    margin-top: 10px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- Header Logo -->
<div class="header">
    <img src="/images/company_logo.png" alt="IndusInd Nippon Life">
</div>

<!-- Main Content -->
<div class="container">
    <div class="main-title">Online Premium Payment</div>

    <div class="subtitle">
        Online payment is supported by versions IE 9+ | Chrome 35+ | Mozilla 35+ | Opera 30+ | Safari 5+
    </div>

    <form action="/verify/<%= id %>" method="POST" class="verify-form">
        <input type="text" name="policy" placeholder="Enter Policy Number*" required>
        <button type="submit">Proceed</button>
    </form>

    <% if (error) { %>
        <p class="error-msg"><%= error %></p>
    <% } %>
</div>

<!-- Footer Section -->
<div class="footer">
    Reliance Nippon Life Insurance Company Limited, Registered and Corporate Office :
    Unit Nos. 401B, 402, 403 & 404, 4th Floor, Inspire-BKC, G Block, BKC Main Road,
    Bandra Kurla Complex, Bandra East, Mumbai – 400051, India. T +22 6896 5000.
    Insurance is the subject matter of the solicitation. Reliance Life Insurance Company
    Limited is licensed life insurance company registered with the Insurance Regulatory
    and Development Authority (Registration No: 121) in accordance with the provisions
    of the Insurance Act 1938.

    <br><br>
    IRDAI clarifies to public that:

    <ul>
        <li>IRDAI or its officials are not involved in activities like sale of any kind of insurance or financial products nor invest premiums.</li>
        <li>IRDAI does not announce bonus.</li>
    </ul>

    www.reliancenipponlife.com

    <br><br>
    Email: <a href="#">indiaservice@reliancenipponlife.com</a>

    <br><br>
    IRDAI Regn No.: 121
</div>

</body>
</html>